        "email": "di.wang@intel.com",
        "username": "wangdi",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-11-16 03:58:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nOh, I put DOT_LUSTRE check there just thought client does not need go further if it is special FID. But it seems I was wrong here,  I will remove this, current FLD can definitely handle this.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
    },
